.id}:`, error);\n42:               }\n43:             }\n\n(End of file - total 43 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"name: Workflow Approval\n\non:\n  pull_request_target:\n    types: [labeled, synchronize]\n    branches:\n      - main\n      - 'release-*'\n\npermissions:\n  actions: write\n  pull-requests: read\n\njobs:\n  approve:\n    name: Approve Workflows for Contributors\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    timeout-minutes: 10\n\n    steps:","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.github/workflows/approve.yml","time":{"start":1775886175312,"end":1775886175331}}}}
