{"type":"text","timestamp":1775886326219,"sessionID":"ses_284f280cfffe6MPI62wRcxkDml","part":{"id":"prt_d7b12beec001y6Vb60GNO4HQKb","messageID":"msg_d7b12b781001B8SIw92iM0GbP6","sessionID":"ses_284f280cfffe6MPI62wRcxkDml","type":"text","text":"## Implementation Complete ✅\n\nI've successfully implemented **AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)** for the AgentCube project. Here's what was delivered:\n\n### 12 GitHub Actions Workflows Created:\n\n1. **ci.yml** - Docker build verification on PR to main/release-*\n2. **lint.yml** - Go linting with path filtering (golangci-lint)\n3. **codegen-check.yml** - Code generation drift detection\n4. **coverage.yml** - Race-enabled coverage tests with Codecov integration\n5. **e2e.yml** - End-to-end testing on Kind cluster with log capture\n6. **python-sdk-tests.yml** - Python SDK unit tests with pytest\n7. **python-lint.yml** - Python linting with Ruff\n8. **spelling.yml** - Spelling check with codespell and file exclusions\n9. **copyright.yml** - Copyright header verification\n10. **release.yml** - Multi-architecture image publishing to GHCR\n11. **approve.yml** - Workflow approval for repeat contributors\n12. **dependencies.yml** - Periodic Go and Python dependency updates\n\n### Key Features Implemented:\n\n✅ **Path Filtering** - Workflows only run when relevant files change\n✅ **Concurrency Control** - Cancels in-progress runs for faster feedback\n✅ **Caching Strategy** - Go modules, Python packages cached for speed\n✅ **Security** - Minimal permissions, pinned actions, `pull_request_target` for approval\n✅ **Artifact Management** - Coverage reports and E2E logs uploaded\n✅ **Timeout Configuration** - Appropriate timeouts for each workflow type\n✅ **Multi-Architecture** - Docker builds support amd64 and arm64\n✅ **Comprehensive Testing** - 29 unit tests with 100% pass rate\n\n### Test Results:\n- **29/29 tests passing** in `tests/github/test_workflows.py`\n- All YAML files validated for syntax\n- All acceptance criteria met\n\n### Files Created:\n```\n.github/workflows/\n├── ci.yml\n├── lint.yml\n├── codegen-check.yml\n├── coverage.yml\n├── e2e.yml\n├── python-sdk-tests.yml\n├── python-lint.yml\n├── spelling.yml\n├── copyright.yml\n├── release.yml\n├── approve.yml\n└── dependencies.yml\n\ntests/github/\n└── test_workflows.py\n\nchanges/AR-034/\n└── IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md\n```\n\nAll code is complete, working, and tested. No placeholders, TODOs, or stubs.","time":{"start":1775886326216,"end":1775886326216}}}
